{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Really rural, that I could stay, we could stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People had already been, we found out later, staying there, a couple of Jewish people, a, a Nazi woman with her two children who had no place to live.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were just-- the place was so big, she allowed various people there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a baroness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Von Hulesen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually her son, I'm, I'm told, I was involved in the attempt on Hitler's life, the, the last one with the bomb planted.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when that failed, that attempt, they eventually quartered the German army there on the property, where I landed, because they suspected he would try to escape to his mother's estate and hide in the rural part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, they did not find him there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we meanwhile had the army on our necks, which was another danger of a different kind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, it was arranged that I could be sent there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a family staying there, a pastor, who was at the Russian front, his wife, and their three sons, ages 14, 12, and my age, five, by then.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think I even have a photograph of little Martin and me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those people were named Bunke, B-U-N-K-E, Frieda Bunke and-- I can't-- he was Pastor Bunke, Pastor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the children's names, I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't care to say them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know where they are now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The wall is down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had been left in East Germany eventually when the war ended.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I would rather not say all that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A woman came to the main train station in Berlin, Anhalter Bahnhof.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was to accompany me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was someone I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
